data.description: Attention Potential VA Buyers: Incredible VA Assumable Loan at 2.77%!! **Charming Country Living Close to Town Center**This lovely 3BR 3.5BA Cape Cod is enviably located in Dunkirk. The sapphire blue swimming pool - with new liner and cover- and the newly done concrete patio are perfect for all manner of socializing, fun, and relaxation. Enjoy this pair of features in privacy, thanks to the rear fencing of the attractively landscaped yard. A breezy front porch is a nice spot for relaxing with beverage and book. Rewards also await on the other side of the Welcome mat. Board gamers, book readers, and mid-day nappers will find picturesque warmth in the glow of a wood burning fireplace in the living room. The renovated gourmet kitchen offers practical functionality in an efficient layout with new premium appliances. The ensuite primary bedroom is conveniently located on the main floor. The upstairs, with new carpet, boasts two welcoming bedrooms and a hall bathroom. The renovated split-unit walkout basement, with the convenience of a full bathroom & kitchen, can be used as an office, rec room, or guest sleeping quarters. Basement makes for a great in-law suite.   Only a short 3-minute drive to the shopping/dining options of Shoppes at Apple Greene and town center. Easy access to Rt4. After your local excursions, you'll return to the sturdy, symmetrical elegance of Cape Cod architecture in a popular location. Out front, the circular driveway has ample room for visitors' parking while the carport offers shelter for your vehicle. Freshly painted and move-in ready! This gorgeous home is the right place at the right time for you.
